sql:
SELECT 
    ds.Document_Subset_ID, 
    ds.Document_Subset_Name, 
    COUNT(DISTINCT dsm.Document_Object_ID) AS num_documents
FROM Document_Subsets ds
JOIN Document_Subset_Members dsm ON ds.Document_Subset_ID = dsm.Document_Subset_ID
GROUP BY ds.Document_Subset_ID, ds.Document_Subset_Name
ORDER BY num_documents DESC
LIMIT 1;

sql:
SELECT d.Document_Subset_ID, d.Document_Subset_Name, COUNT(DISTINCT m.Document_Object_ID) AS number_of_documents
FROM Document_Subsets d
JOIN Document_Subset_Members m ON d.Document_Subset_ID = m.Document_Subset_ID
GROUP BY d.Document_Subset_ID, d.Document_Subset_Name
ORDER BY number_of_documents DESC
LIMIT 1;

FROM Document_Subset_Members dsm
JOIN Document_Subsets ds ON dsm.Document_Subset_ID = ds.Document_Subset_ID
GROUP BY dsm.Document_Subset_ID, ds.Document_Subset_Name
ORDER BY document_count DESC
LIMIT 1;
